description:
If dyke jocks, soccer uniforms, and SWEAT make you hot and bothered… You won’t want to miss LESBIAN SOCCER LUST!

Soccer Superstars Lena Harrington and Lexi Guerrero may be rivals on the field but they are loving girlfriends off it.

Watch soccer’s most iconic pair discuss the importance of SKILL VS STAMINA—right before Lena makes Lexi LICK HER CLEAT, showing her partner who’s boss on this turf.

Dont miss Part 1 of the MONDO FETICHE DERBY and you’ll see why they call it THE BEAUTIFUL GAME!

Starring PLAYMAKER and FAN FAVORITE AVA D’AMORE and introducing YOUNG PROMISE LUCY STRAWBERRY!
title: Lesbian Soccer Lust
